<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>化學實驗室暴露評估資訊圖表</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
            background-color: #F0F4F8; 
        }
        .chart-container {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            height: 300px;
            max-height: 400px;
        }
        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .chart-container {
                height: 350px;
            }
        }
        .kpi-value {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }
        .kpi-unit {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-left: 0.5rem;
        }
        .flow-arrow {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #FF6B6B;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-gray-800">

    <!-- Palette: Energetic & Playful (#FF6B6B, #FFD166, #06D6A0, #118AB2, #073B4C) -->
    <!-- Plan: 
        1. Header: Title and introduction.
        2. Section 1: The Assessment Journey (Flowchart). Goal: Organize. Method: HTML/CSS. Justification: Clearly shows the process steps. NO SVG.
        3. Section 2: Initial Deterministic Model. Goal: Inform/Compare. Method: Big Number & Bar Chart (Chart.js). Justification: Highlights the single-point estimate and compares it to the OEL. NO SVG.
        4. Section 3: Introducing Variability. Goal: Compare. Method: Bar Chart (Chart.js). Justification: Compares best, worst, and initial scenarios effectively. NO SVG.
        5. Section 4: Probabilistic Modeling (Monte Carlo). Goal: Relationships/Inform. Method: Histogram (Chart.js) & Big Number. Justification: Shows the full distribution of possible outcomes and highlights the key 95th percentile metric. NO SVG.
        6. Section 5: The Final Verdict. Goal: Inform/Compare. Method: Donut Chart (Chart.js) & summary text. Justification: Provides a clear, final comparison of the key metric against the safety limit. NO SVG.
    -->
    <!-- Confirmation: NEITHER Mermaid JS NOR SVG were used anywhere in this output. -->

    <div class="container mx-auto p-4 md:p-8">

        <header class="text-center mb-12">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[#073B4C] mb-4">化學實驗室暴露評估之旅</h1>
            <p class="text-lg font-bold text-red-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">從點估計到機率性分析：有機化學實驗室中二氯甲烷暴露風險評估。</p>
        </header>

        <main class="space-y-12">

            <section id="journey" class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 md:p-8">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#118AB2] mb-6 text-center">評估的演進之路</h2>
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-4 text-center">
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-4">
                        <div class="text-4xl mb-2">🤔</div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-[#073B4C]">質化疑慮</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">溶劑氣味明顯</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flow-arrow transform md:-rotate-0">→</div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg">
                        <div class="text-4xl mb-2">📊</div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-[#073B4C]">確定性模型</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">單點最差估計</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flow-arrow transform md:-rotate-0">→</div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-4">
                        <div class="text-4xl mb-2">📈</div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-[#073B4C]">範圍分析</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">最佳/最差情境</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flow-arrow transform md:-rotate-0">→</div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg">
                        <div class="text-4xl mb-2">🎲</div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-[#073B4C]">機率性模型</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">蒙地卡羅模擬</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flow-arrow transform md:-rotate-0">→</div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center p-4">
                        <div class="text-4xl mb-2">✅</div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-[#073B4C]">風險決策</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">可防禦的結論</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 md:p-8">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#118AB2] mb-2">1. 確定性模型：一個警訊</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">此模型基於一系列保守的「最差情境」假設（如滿班24人、溶劑完全蒸發），快速評估潛在風險。這是一個必要的起點，用於判斷是否需要進一步調查。</p>
                    <div class="text-center my-8">
                        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">計算出的穩態濃度</p>
                        <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center text-[#FF6B6B]">
                            <span class="kpi-value">110</span>
                            <span class="kpi-unit">mg/m³</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="chart-container h-64 md:h-72">
                        <canvas id="deterministicChart"></canvas>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">初步計算結果顯著高於8小時容許暴露限值（PEL），觸發了進一步分析的必要性。</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 md:p-8">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#118AB2] mb-2">2. 引入變異性：更廣的視野</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">透過與現場人員訪談，我們了解到實際情況充滿變數（如學生人數、溶劑蒸發量、換氣率）。此分析界定了暴露濃度的可能範圍，但未能說明範圍內各值的發生機率。</p>
                    <div class="chart-container h-96 md:h-auto">
                        <canvas id="rangeChart"></canvas>
                    </div>
                     <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">最差情境下的暴露濃度（106 mg/m³）依然很高，但最佳情境（6.7 mg/m³）則遠低於標準。這揭示了風險並非恆定不變。</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <section id="monte-carlo" class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 md:p-8 md:col-span-2">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[red] mb-2 text-center">3. 機率性模型：描繪真實輪廓</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">蒙地卡羅模擬是本次評估的核心。它運行了10,000次電腦模擬，每次都從代表真實變異的機率分佈中隨機抽取參數。這不僅告訴我們「可能發生什麼」，更重要的是「各種情況發生的可能性有多大」。</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-center">
                    <div class="md:col-span-2 chart-container h-80 md:h-96">
                        <canvas id="monteCarloChart"></canvas>
                        <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">模擬結果呈現對數常態分佈，這與真實世界的職業暴露數據特徵相符。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-2">關鍵指標：<br>第95百分位數</p>
                        <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center text-[#06D6A0]">
                            <span class="kpi-value">57</span>
                            <span class="kpi-unit">mg/m³</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">這代表了一個統計上穩健的「合理最高暴露」。根據模型，有95%的機率，暴露濃度會低於此數值。這是比平均值或單一最差情境更可靠的決策依據。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section id="verdict" class="bg-[#073B4C] text-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 md:p-8">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6 text-center">4. 最終結論：一個可防禦的決策</h2>
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
                    <div class="w-full md:w-2/3">
                        <p class="text-lg mb-4">經過精細的機率性分析，我們得出結論：實驗室的暴露水平在絕大多數（95%）可預見的情況下，均低於法規的8小時容許暴露限值（87~mg/m^3）。</p>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">這個從 110~mg/m^3 到 57~mg/m^3 的分析過程，展示了擁抱並量化不確定性的價值。它避免了基於過度保守假設可能導致的「假陽性」警報，並為與利害關係人進行有效溝通提供了堅實的數據基礎。</p>
                        <p class="font-bold text-[#FFD166]">最終評估：暴露風險在目前的操作條件下是可接受的，但仍建議透過加強學生操作培訓來進一步降低潛在的峰值暴露。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full md:w-1/3">
                        <div class="chart-container h-64">
                            <canvas id="finalVerdictChart"></canvas>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>

        <footer class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-12 py-4 border-t">
            <p>參考CH12 Lab Exposure of MC modeling. made by Petert Ho. 114.08.18</p>
        </footer>

    </div>

    <script>
        function wrapLabels(label) {
            if (typeof label === 'string' && label.length > 16) {
                const words = label.split(' ');
                const lines = [];
                let currentLine = '';
                words.forEach(word => {
                    if ((currentLine + word).length > 16) {
                        lines.push(currentLine.trim());
                        currentLine = '';
                    }
                    currentLine += word + ' ';
                });
                lines.push(currentLine.trim());
                return lines;
            }
            return label;
        }

        const tooltipTitleCallback = function(tooltipItems) {
            const item = tooltipItems[0];
            let label = item.chart.data.labels[item.dataIndex];
            if (Array.isArray(label)) {
                return label.join(' ');
            } else {
                return label;
            }
        };
        
        const PEL_VALUE = 87;
        const PALETTE = {
            red: '#FF6B6B',
            yellow: '#FFD166',
            green: '#06D6A0',
            blue: '#118AB2',
            darkBlue: '#073B4C',
            gray: '#6B7280'
        };

        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
            
            new Chart(document.getElementById('deterministicChart'), {
                type: 'bar',
                data: {
                    labels: ['模型估計濃度', '8小時容許暴露限值 (PEL)'],
                    datasets: [{
                        label: '濃度 (mg/m³)',
                        data: [110, PEL_VALUE],
                        backgroundColor: [PALETTE.red, PALETTE.blue],
                        borderColor: [PALETTE.red, PALETTE.blue],
                        borderWidth: 1
                    }]
                },
                options: {
                    responsive: true,
                    maintainAspectRatio: false,
                    indexAxis: 'y',
                    scales: {
                        x: {
                            beginAtZero: true,
                            title: { display: true, text: '濃度 (mg/m³)' }
                        }
                    },
                    plugins: {
                        legend: { display: false },
                        tooltip: { callbacks: { title: tooltipTitleCallback } }
                    }
                }
            });

            new Chart(document.getElementById('rangeChart'), {
                type: 'bar',
                data: {
                    labels: ['最佳情境', '最差情境', wrapLabels('初始確定性模型')],
                    datasets: [{
                        label: '濃度 (mg/m³)',
                        data: [6.7, 106, 110],
                        backgroundColor: [PALETTE.green, PALETTE.red, PALETTE.yellow],
                    }, {
                        type: 'line',
                        label: '8小時容許暴露限值 (PEL)',
                        data: [PEL_VALUE, PEL_VALUE, PEL_VALUE],
                        borderColor: PALETTE.darkBlue,
                        borderWidth: 2,
                        pointRadius: 0,
                        fill: false,
                        borderDash: [5, 5]
                    }]
                },
                options: {
                    responsive: true,
                    maintainAspectRatio: false,
                    scales: {
                        y: {
                            beginAtZero: true,
                            title: { display: true, text: '濃度 (mg/m³)' }
                        }
                    },
                    plugins: {
                        legend: { position: 'bottom' },
                        tooltip: { callbacks: { title: tooltipTitleCallback } }
                    }
                }
            });

            const monteCarloData = Array.from({length: 10000}, (_, i) => {
                const u1 = Math.random();
                const u2 = Math.random();
                const z = Math.sqrt(-2.0 * Math.log(u1)) * Math.cos(2.0 * Math.PI * u2);
                const studentEvap = 185 + 30 * z;
                const numStudents = Math.floor(Math.random() * (24 - 12 + 1)) + 12;
                const ventilation = 67 + Math.random() * (133 - 67);
                const totalEmission = numStudents * studentEvap;
                const concentration = totalEmission / ventilation;
                return Math.max(0, concentration); 
            }).sort((a, b) => a - b);

            const bins = {};
            for (let i = 0; i < 120; i += 5) {
                bins[i] = 0;
            }
            monteCarloData.forEach(val => {
                const bin = Math.floor(val / 5) * 5;
                if (bins[bin] !== undefined) {
                    bins[bin]++;
                }
            });

            new Chart(document.getElementById('monteCarloChart'), {
                type: 'bar',
                data: {
                    labels: Object.keys(bins),
                    datasets: [{
                        label: '模擬次數',
                        data: Object.values(bins),
                        backgroundColor: PALETTE.blue,
                        barPercentage: 1.0,
                        categoryPercentage: 1.0
                    }, {
                        type: 'line',
                        label: '第95百分位數 (57 mg/m³)',
                        data: Array(Object.keys(bins).length).fill(null).map((_, i) => (parseFloat(Object.keys(bins)[i]) === 55 ? 500 : null)),
                        borderColor: PALETTE.green,
                        borderWidth: 3,
                        fill: false,
                        pointRadius: 0,
                        borderDash: [6, 6]
                    }]
                },
                options: {
                    responsive: true,
                    maintainAspectRatio: false,
                    scales: {
                        x: {
                            title: { display: true, text: '濃度區間 (mg/m³)' },
                            ticks: {
                                callback: function(value, index, values) {
                                    return index % 2 === 0 ? this.getLabelForValue(value) : '';
                                }
                            }
                        },
                        y: {
                            title: { display: true, text: '頻率 (10,000次模擬)' }
                        }
                    },
                    plugins: {
                        legend: { display: false },
                        tooltip: { callbacks: { title: tooltipTitleCallback } }
                    }
                }
            });

            new Chart(document.getElementById('finalVerdictChart'), {
                type: 'doughnut',
                data: {
                    labels: ['安全緩衝區', '第95百分位數暴露'],
                    datasets: [{
                        data: [PEL_VALUE - 57, 57],
                        backgroundColor: [PALETTE.blue, PALETTE.green],
                        borderColor: '#073B4C',
                        borderWidth: 4,
                        hoverOffset: 4
                    }]
                },
                options: {
                    responsive: true,
                    maintainAspectRatio: false,
                    cutout: '70%',
                    plugins: {
                        legend: { 
                            position: 'bottom',
                            labels: { color: 'white' }
                        },
                        title: {
                            display: true,
                            text: '第95百分位數 vs. 容許暴露限值',
                            color: 'white',
                            font: { size: 14 }
                        },
                        tooltip: { callbacks: { title: tooltipTitleCallback } }
                    }
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
